title: Symposium of Undergraduate Robotics, Engineering & IT
excerpt: Join SUREI to explore innovative robotics, engineering, and IT projects, showcase your work, and network with students, academics, and industry leaders!
description: SUREI is a project showcase where undergraduate students present their work in robotics, engineering, and IT. Compete for amazing prizes: 1st place $300, 2nd place $200, 3rd place $100, and People’s Choice LEGO prize. Network with industry leaders, showcase your projects, and gain inspiration from peers and professionals alike. Tickets available here: https://events.humanitix.com/symposium-of-undergraduate-robotics-and-electrical-engineering
